&lt;li&gt;Identify trends in payer behavior and surface them for leadership review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with various departments to resolve open accounts, including: clinical to appeal medical necessity denials, accounting for cash posting and reconciliation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
