&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated Application Security Engineer who is looking to help build the maturity of our Application Security Team while growing their own security skill set. Our team prioritizes the full lifecycle of security triage: identifying vulnerabilities, reproducing exploits, meticulous code analysis, and crafting production-ready fixes. We are looking for an engineer with good attention to detail, the ability to learn quickly and pick up new skills independently, and a get-things-done attitude with eagerness to build something awesome!&lt;/p&gt;
